  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this survey is to assess patients with chronic primary or secondary adrenal
      failure regarding subjective health status, incidence and causes of adrenal crisis, hormone
      replacement regimens and concomitant endocrine or non endocrine disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
